! 矩阵操作
---

!! 寻找最大值

```matlab
[a,b] = find(matrix == min(min(matrix)));
% or
[a,b] = find(matrix == min(matrix(:)));
```

!! APPEND 数组添加值

```matlab
array = [array a];
```

!! 限制矩阵内的值

将矩阵的值限制在(min,max)内。

```matlab
m(m > max) = max;
m(m < min) = min;
```